Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.61,Title3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,385)}Searching for the Full Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:13.37,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The road to love is far too long for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:18.26,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way for me to love you any more. Nope, Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:22.12,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if the world inside my dream is a completely different one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:26.52,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,where I can even tell you how I really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:35.80,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wear my favorite clothes every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:43.56,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,so that person will turn his gaze towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:48.07,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I like you" If I could bring myself to say it out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:52.44,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would even be able to talk about love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.83,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be tucked into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:01.12,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will do anything to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:05.46,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you" Those are the words I want to hear from you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.01,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,and my breath will quicken when we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:18.97,OP 01 - Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,The me who is performing for you is the cutest of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.24,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someday... somehow, someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:44.45,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, no matter where,\N I'm going to do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left at my disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:55.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}And now, everything's getting out of hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.45,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.94,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's the last song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:21.62,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.08,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.79,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream of becoming a singer finally came true, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.80,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:31.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:31.88,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.41,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I... love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.17,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Eichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.20,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Eichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.70,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.24,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Eichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:10.25,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}NO MATTER WHAT, I WANT TO SING!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:15.29,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, won't you look up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:20.26,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky tonight is so wide and spacious after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:25.22,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.15,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:36.09,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky tonight is so wide and spacious after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.38,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.03,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.05,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told you to stop doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.63,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Music is such a vile thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.75,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of your father, it makes me feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.73,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.33,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.97,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Has your fever gone down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.68,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.63,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Wakaouji is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.20,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.39,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Wakaouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for calling you in during your vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.51,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's her health?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.52,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be doing much better this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.38,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.57,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.84,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's swelled up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.51,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I apply treatment on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:36.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.77,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.67,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.67,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Dr. Wakaouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.13,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:50.99,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we pretend that you're taking me to the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.05,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You need an excuse to get out of the house, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.85,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where do you plan on going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.95,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Seed Records' Debut Artist Audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Notification of Passing the First Review!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.15,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm keeping this a secret from Grandma, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:09.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.50,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had a fever yesterday and\Nhad to leave school early, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.33,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Your throat is swollen and as your doctor, I can't allow you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:20.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I finally managed to get past the first review...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In your current condition, you can't sing in a loud voice, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.36,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You can think about auditioning\Nafter your throat gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.44,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:35.48,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,While it's still small, let's try an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.70,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:41.44,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I might lose my voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.20,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cross that bridge when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.43,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee that it won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.49,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I don't want to be operated on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.95,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:55.90,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What's even more terrifying than dying is not being able to sing for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.27,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:05:59.92,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.80,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam... it's about Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.23,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you possibly convince her, to go through with the operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.89,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already suggested it time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.56,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...she still refuses to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.30,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,For heaven's sake... She's just as stubborn as my late daughter was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.77,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She is unable to give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.89,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Another failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:33.41,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll have to wait\Nuntil my throat gets better...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Mitsuki, let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:49.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Until we meet again, we'll work hard to reach our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.04,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll become an astronomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(0,1400)}And you'll become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.93,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Okay? It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.97,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:07:01.26,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But... just when will that happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Eichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.59,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.37,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you come out of the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.02,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuki Kouyama, age 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.00,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does he know my name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.51,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Takuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-Another one came out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.45,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are these people?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.45,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to lose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.49,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.13,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the kind of attitude you show towards your senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.45,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to bring up your seniority every time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.80,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.97,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Who might... you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Can see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:48.63,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.16,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why can she see us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.71,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans who are still living shouldn't be able to see us, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:56.03,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.03,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.79,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do in this kind of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.29,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come to this, we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:00.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.48,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.46,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absurd to remain unknown when our cover is blown...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Shinigami, the ones who silence the tears of children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.44,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.71,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Meroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.24,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.35,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.94,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You call yourselves Negi Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds so tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:22.90,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.22,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't stand our duo's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.05,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.20,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Our chief chose it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:32.86,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Bunny ears and kitty ears... So soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.50,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we're in the Pediatrics Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.64,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Pediatrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.33,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami have kids, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.54,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, if you're Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.36,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.54,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what were here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.13,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.24,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.40,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend you didn't hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to die for one more year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.68,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,One more year?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.64,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because... my cancer gets worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.15,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that could be why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.10,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Please, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.00,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.57,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, while we have the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... In times like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.49,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:18.70,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there are people who are trying to prevent your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.54,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'm not going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It doesn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.16,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate cannot be altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.15,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.88,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I only have one year left to live,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hesitate any longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.67,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you shut up! What are you trying to accomplish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to report this to the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.76,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we've already been seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.41,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if after a year passes, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.61,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.74,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.31,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.70,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.00,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.33,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.56,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.35,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I had almost caught up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.62,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.74,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.33,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Shinigami, thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to take the audition now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.74,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I only have a year left,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:35.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll definitely become a singer before then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.78,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is it, Eichi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The promise we made...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.30,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep it for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.28,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought she was a good girl, so we let her get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:22.74,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.20,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.69,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.71,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.66,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just go up to her like that, she'll run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.17,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.51,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.42,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a key around here somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.80,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.45,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get up there then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.51,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.48,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.94,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem a little... out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.48,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.78,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.89,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's troublesome for us when you go running off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, be a good girl and come\Nback to the house with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:11.67,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.73,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go through the audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.42,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to just go home like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why were you trying to go in from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.62,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Why not just use the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:27.28,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't because I don't look like I'm sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.41,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I'm sixteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.35,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... no, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.16,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, I'm going in through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:37.77,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it, you dummy! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.06,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:43.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't hurry, the audition will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.80,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have to become a singe-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.16,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.20,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking... loudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.51,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.01,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,My throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.66,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, isn't it impossible for you to audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.38,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.76,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.79,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If I only have one year left to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.14,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,please, at least let me audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.45,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If I fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.44,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a good girl and do what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.02,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.56,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.23,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious about this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.96,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you sixteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.15,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, as long as you're sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.15,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it so your body is healthy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:37.92,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.88,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,On my command, that will begin spreading inside of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.46,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel weird, but you'll just have to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.86,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.91,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't feel the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.77,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.90,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Check yourself out over there, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.01,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really sixteen years old!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.87,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.05,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.05,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.69,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get away from Takuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.41,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.96,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I want to try dying my hair, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Takuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.69,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disobeying our orders from above by letting a human know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:56.12,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out, you'll be in for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.12,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.62,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... You... and her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.60,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.52,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.99,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.78,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let her have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.63,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when was I your possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.05,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.09,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If she still has any regrets left, and she passes away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.77,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If she refuses to come with us, it'll be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.47,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.50,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if she makes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.00,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have even more to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.31,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she can make it just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.89,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,After turning sixteen and going through an audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:30.28,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,only to fail and to have to face reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.84,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't have a shred of regret left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.78,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:41.67,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the girls here are really cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.67,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I look too plain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's staring at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.40,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I look too strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.90,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I'm out of fashion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.49,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:19.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What agency are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:23.36,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not part of a theatrical group or a recording agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:23.92,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:29.14,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me I won't make it if I'm not part of an agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.63,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather unfortunate, but it's probably impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.09,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.28,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They've already chosen someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:37.96,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.04,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why are we auditioning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.04,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm very sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.62,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.42,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:53.24,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This audition gets lots of coverage on the morning news and on talk shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:59.52,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Media exposure will help anyone winning the audition become overnight sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.84,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's their one and only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.27,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.72,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You... already knew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.13,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.00,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The judging you've all been waiting for will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.60,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.64,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in when your number is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.93,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,To start, will Number 1 please come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's how it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.10,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel kinda... let down...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:28.95,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought this was a world based more on talent than anything else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:32.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don't say that you want to be a singer ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.61,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandma always discouraged me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You should wait until your throat is better before you audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:39.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Wakaouji tried to stop me, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.70,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You have one more year before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.88,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,1200)}One more year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.33,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I... here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eichi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 21, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.43,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Number 21, Mitsuki Kouyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.39,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.73,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What genre of music do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.41,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I like... Japanese pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:08.58,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If you became a singer, is there anything in particular you 'd like to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:09.56,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just want to sing since I like singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.62,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing for us then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.49,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Cue the music, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:23.61,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's that nervous, there's no way she'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:30.79,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing that will never ever change...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.50,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, stop for a second. Your voice is too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.50,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream I am--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.38,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.06,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Louder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.50,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.54,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's impossible for you to sing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.81,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.88,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.31,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.81,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to run away like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.37,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Your throat is fine, so sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.59,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You love to sing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.64,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You really love singing, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.95,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.49,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I love to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:10.42,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.19,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please let me try one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.25,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.38,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Cue the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.53,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's fine if it's painful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.82,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much it hurts inside...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.03,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's pain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.28,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.35,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all part of my dream!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:32.79,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's till one more thing that will never ever change...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:37.69,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,...the dream that I am always sketching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:42.79,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The me that I am right now, could I possibly reflect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:50.83,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,all of those days in these small eyes of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:20:00.76,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, won't you look up? The sky tonight is so wide and spacious after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:07.03,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... very soon...\Nso I can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.60,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0036,,Wow! I have such a loud voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:10.77,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,With all I've got, I'm going to hurry up and shine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.81,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0036,,It doesn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.06,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0036,,I can sing in a voice like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.65,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.84,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:23.57,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So that we can be together forever, I'm doing everything that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.10,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:34.04,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I will embrace yesterday's fate and tomorrow's hopes inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.88,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:44.01,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm with you, I'll overcome any pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:48.58,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,More and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:53.54,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be even closer to you, I stand here right now and give...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.03,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Many thanks for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.74,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:06.78,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Miya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.74,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Ishikawa, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.18,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.11,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida! Send everyone else back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.35,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided on number 21!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:11.95,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:12.93,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what should we do about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been chosen?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.55,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Although previously expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:23.21,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,there will not be a third judging.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.01,Primary Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.29,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-What should I do, Eichi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.98,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made it!{\i0}
