Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:08.30,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done, Takuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:10.32,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl made it, didn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.64,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet! I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:13.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.38,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fallen in love with that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:17.02,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:18.04,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:20.87,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl has someone named Eichi, whom she likes a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:24.34,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She's becoming a singer because of a promise with Eichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.23,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.24,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.65,Primary Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because of something like that?!
